---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import GlowLineSeparator from '@/components/ui/separator/GlowLineSeparator.astro';
const pageTitle = 'About Me';
const pageDescription = 'Learn more about my background and approach to software engineering.';
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} pubDate={new Date()} showHeader={false}>
  <p>
    I’m a backend engineer with 7.5+ years of experience building reliable and scalable software systems. I specialize in designing backend services, APIs, and distributed systems that handle real-world scale and complexity. I enjoy solving problems at the architecture level and building systems that are simple, resilient, and maintainable.
  </p>
  <p>
    I’ve worked extensively with technologies like Node.js, Java, Kafka, Redis, and MongoDB to build event-driven and microservice-based systems. My interests include system design, performance optimization, and building backend infrastructure that scales efficiently as products grow.
  </p>
  <p>
    Outside of work, I enjoy building personal projects around distributed systems and scalable platforms. I’m also passionate about sports and gaming, and interested in building technology that creates opportunities in sports and esports communities.
  </p>

  <GlowLineSeparator />

</Layout>
